OL,3,CPSNI civilian staff set for industrial
OL,4,Caction over danger money pay
OL,6,FPolice civilian staff in Northern
OL,7,FIreland are set to take part in strike
OL,8,Faction over an ongoing failure to
OL,9,Fincrease danger money payments.
OL,11,FThe workers are expected to stage a 24-
OL,12,Fhour walk out from 0001 on July 11 to
OL,13,F0001 on July 12.
OL,15,FIt will come just before tens of
OL,16,Fthousands of people take to the
OL,17,Fstreets for the annual Orange Order
OL,18,Fparades on July 12.
