OL,6,FThe trade union NIPSA said its members
OL,7,F"overwhelmingly voted for strike
OL,8,Faction" over their Revised
OL,9,FEnvironmental Allowance (REA).
OL,11,FPolice civilian staff are calling for
OL,12,Fthe delivery of an uplift to their
OL,13,F#580 annual REA, known as danger money
OL,14,Fallowance, that was committed to five
OL,15,Fyears ago.
OL,17,FIn comparison, PSNI officers currently
OL,18,Freceive just under #4,000 annually in
OL,19,Facknowledgement of the ongoing threat
OL,20,Fthey face.
