OL,3,CPSNI civilian staff set for industrial
OL,4,Caction over danger money pay
OL,6,FCivilian staff, who are seeking to
OL,7,Fhave their allowance increased to
OL,8,Faround #1,000, are involved in roles
OL,9,Fsuch as emergency call handling and
OL,10,Fscenes of crime work.
OL,12,FNIPSA said 91% voted for strike action
OL,13,Fand 96% voted for action short of
OL,14,Fstrike.
OL,16,FThe union said the civilian workers
OL,17,Ffeel they are under threat and
OL,18,Fundervalued, and are working in an
OL,19,F"effectively created two-tier
OL,20,Fworkforce" due to the disparities in
OL,21,Fpay and terms and conditions.
