OL,6,FAction short of strike is set to start
OL,7,Fat the beginning of July.
OL,9,FPSNI temporary assistant chief
OL,10,Fconstable Melanie Jones said they want
OL,11,Fto assure the public that they will
OL,12,Fhave resources in place to keep the
OL,13,Fpublic safe.
OL,15,F"Planning is under way to mitigate any
OL,16,Frisk in critical functions in the
OL,17,Fevent of staff absences as a result of
OL,18,Fthis industrial action," she said.
